    The callback executor used to run the Promise.listen(Listener) and Promise.onClose(CloseListener) callbacks.

    Result.Chain<T1,E extends java.lang.Exception,R>
    A listener to use for Promise.then(me.tatarka.ipromise.func.Chain) that gives two callbacks for success and failure.
    Result.ChainPromise<T1,T2,E extends java.lang.Exception>

    Result.ChainResult<T1,T2,E extends java.lang.Exception>

    Result.Listener<T,E extends java.lang.Exception>
